        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 border-b pb-2">â• æ–°å¢å›è¦†è¦å‰‡</h3>
                <div class="space-y-4">
